<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #f7fafc;
      color: #2d3748;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .cancel-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 50px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cancel-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      font-size: 50px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #718096;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-box {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .info-box p {
      color: #92400e;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .info-box p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: #667eea;
      border: 2px solid #667eea;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f7fafc;
    }

    .support-note {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .support-note h3 {
      color: #2d3748;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .support-note p {
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .cancel-container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .btn-group {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .btn {
        min-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="cancel-container">
    <div class="cancel-icon">⏸️</div>

    <h1>Checkout Cancelled</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      No charges were made to your account.
    </p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <p><strong>What happened?</strong></p>
      <p>You closed the checkout page or clicked the back button before completing your purchase.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px;">Your trial status remains unchanged, and you can try again whenever you're ready.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="support-note">
      <h3>Need help deciding?</h3>
      <p>
        We understand choosing a subscription is a big decision. Here's what FilterFive can do for your business:
      </p>
      <ul style="text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 2;">
        <li>✓ Filter negative reviews before they go public</li>
        <li>✓ Automatically collect positive reviews on Google</li>
        <li>✓ Send feedback requests via SMS or QR code</li>
        <li>✓ Build trust and grow your online reputation</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/dashboard/subscription" class="btn btn-primary">
        View Plans Again
      </a>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">
        Back to Dashboard
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #a0aec0; font-size: 13px;">
      Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@filterfive.io" style="color: #667eea;">info@filterfive.io</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
